      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>fresh tagliatelle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> tagliatelle</strong> for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>tagliatelle</strong>, reserving 100ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> [200ml] </span>of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
