      "instruction": "<p>Wash, then chop your <strong>cavolo nero</strong> roughly, removing any tough stalks</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cavolo nero</strong> to the pan with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the cavolo nero has wilted</p>",
